    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
たとふれば戦ひ果てぬ、<lb />
日は暮れて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">二時</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふたとき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を経ぬ<lb />
なまぐさき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">荒野</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あらの</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">中</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">双</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の眼を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">弾丸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に射られて<lb />
なほ黒き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">呻吟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うめき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をしのび、<lb />
よこたはる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">負傷</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いたで</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の兵の<lb />
勇しきわかき心に、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">秘</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>めつゝむ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">苦痛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くるしみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">遂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鈍色</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">にびいろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寂寞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じやくまく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">気</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">き</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<lb />
吸ふがごと嗚呼われこゝに。<lb />
<lb />
くらがりの冷えたる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">室</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">むろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
ひとり居ておもひ沈めば、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">空想</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くうさう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">蠑螺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さゞえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">殻</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">から</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
底つ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">闇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たどるがごとく、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鬱憂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うつゆう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ははた<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">南蛮</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なんばん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>深き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">荒磯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ありそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の上に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鋭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">銛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">もり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">腮</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あぎと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にうけて<lb />
横はる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">粗膚鮫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あらはだざめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">断末魔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だんまつま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>――濁りゆく<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">眼</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">め</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">無辺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">むへん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なる闇を見るごと。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">愛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>消えし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の心は<lb />
霜の夜の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">渚</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なぎさ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひぢ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
まみれたる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寄居蟹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">がうな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">殻</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">から</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
冷やかに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">凍</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れたるごとし、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">土色</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つちいろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にはた<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青銅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せいどう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">巨鐘</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おほがね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">銹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のやうなる<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寂寞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じやくまく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">五百重</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いほへ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のなかに<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">一瞬</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いつしゆん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も千とせのおもひ、<lb />
あゝかゝる日の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">凶時</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まがどき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
人は死に、花は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">萎</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しを</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れめ。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
